name: Zunesha / ズニーシャ
description:
Zunesha is a gargantuan elephant, comparable to an island in sheer scale, its two jointed legs are disproportionately and extremely long, such that it can walk on the sea floor while its upper body, including about a third of each leg, remains above the water.

This work is inspired by the One Piece manga
By Geraldc 2021
